## Screen Resolutions

A collection of different screen resolutions.

- Example:

```js
import "domepunk/graphics/res" for Snes
System.print(Snes.size)
```

---
## [Class Resolution](https://github.com/ninjascl/domepunk/blob/main/domepunk/graphics/res.wren#L19)
